Pillow:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Pillow is a library for image processing in Python and is used for image creation in PDFs.
Pillow is distributed under the HPND License. You can find more information about the HPND License in the provided LICENSE file.

Pillow (HPND License)
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/python-pillow/Pillow/main/LICENSE

====================================================================
fillpdf:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
fillpdf is a library that facilitates data transfer from Python to PDFs.
fillpdf is distributed under the MIT License. 
You can find more information about the MIT License in the provided LICENSE file.

fillpdf (MIT License)
https://github.com/t-houssian/fillpdf/blob/main/LICENSE

